messages.messageBody:
Someone posted here a few days ago about a Baby Doll Backpack Carrier. I
found one for $7.00 at Big Lots here in Tulsa, OK. I don't know if you
have this store in your area or if you can find someone who does, but I
would be willing to help if you need me to. Let me know if you need me
to ship you one.
